trans-unit.source: Stores linked resources to be sent as part of an e-mail message.
trans-unit.target: Butikker koblede ressurser som skal sendes som en del av en e-postmelding.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the LinkedResourceCollection class is returned by the <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av klassen LinkedResourceCollection er returnert av den <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.LinkedResources%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>.</xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection> in an unusable state.

After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection> occupied.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>opptatt.</xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection> </xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: This method invokes <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.Dispose%2A> on all views in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden aktiverer <xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.Dispose%2A>på alle visninger i denne samlingen.</xref:System.Net.Mail.AlternateView.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the <xref:System.Net.Mail.MailMessage.Dispose%2A> method.
You do not need to call it in your application.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger ikke å kalle i programmet.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>.</xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using are not freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker ikke frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.Net.Mail.LinkedResourceCollection>
